{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.1","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:1","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.007.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Recommandations au sujet de la collecte pour les chr\u00e9tiens de J\u00e9rusalem<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-15: cf. Mc 12:41-44. (2 Co 9. Ro 15:25-27.) Ac 11:27-29. 2 Th 2:16, 17.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Nous vous faisons conna\u00eetre, fr\u00e8res, la gr\u00e2ce de Dieu qui s\u2019est manifest\u00e9e dans les \u00c9glises de la Mac\u00e9doine.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.2","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.7.16","name":"2 Corinthiens 7:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.7.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.2","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:2","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Au milieu de beaucoup de tribulations qui les ont \u00e9prouv\u00e9es, leur joie d\u00e9bordante et leur pauvret\u00e9 profonde ont produit avec abondance de riches lib\u00e9ralit\u00e9s de leur part.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.3","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.1","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.3","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:3","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Ils ont, je l\u2019atteste, donn\u00e9 volontairement selon leurs moyens, et m\u00eame au-del\u00e0 de leurs moyens,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.4","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.2","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.4","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:4","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>nous demandant avec de grandes instances la gr\u00e2ce de prendre part \u00e0 l\u2019assistance destin\u00e9e aux saints.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.5","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.3","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.5","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:5","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Et non seulement ils ont contribu\u00e9 comme nous l\u2019esp\u00e9rions, mais ils se sont d\u2019abord donn\u00e9s eux-m\u00eames au Seigneur, puis \u00e0 nous, par la volont\u00e9 de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.6","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.4","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.6","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:6","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Nous avons donc engag\u00e9 Tite \u00e0 achever chez vous cette \u0153uvre de bienfaisance, comme il l\u2019avait commenc\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.7","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.5","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.7","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:7","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>De m\u00eame que vous excellez en toutes choses, en foi, en parole, en connaissance, en z\u00e8le \u00e0 tous \u00e9gards, et dans votre amour pour nous, faites en sorte d\u2019exceller aussi dans cette \u0153uvre de bienfaisance.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.6","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.8","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:8","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Je ne dis pas cela pour donner un ordre, mais pour \u00e9prouver, par le z\u00e8le des autres, la sinc\u00e9rit\u00e9 de votre charit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.9","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.7","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.9","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:9","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Car vous connaissez la gr\u00e2ce de notre Seigneur J\u00e9sus-Christ, qui pour vous s\u2019est fait pauvre, de riche qu\u2019il \u00e9tait, afin que par sa pauvret\u00e9 vous fussiez enrichis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.10","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:10","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>C\u2019est un avis que je donne l\u00e0-dessus, car cela vous convient, \u00e0 vous qui non seulement avez commenc\u00e9 \u00e0 agir, mais qui en avez eu la volont\u00e9 d\u00e8s l\u2019ann\u00e9e derni\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.11","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.9","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.11","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:11","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Achevez donc maintenant d\u2019agir, afin que l\u2019accomplissement selon vos moyens r\u00e9ponde \u00e0 l\u2019empressement que vous avez mis \u00e0 vouloir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.12","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.12","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:12","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>La bonne volont\u00e9, quand elle existe, est agr\u00e9able en raison de ce qu\u2019elle peut avoir \u00e0 sa disposition, et non de ce qu\u2019elle n\u2019a pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.13","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.11","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.13","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:13","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Car il s\u2019agit, non de vous exposer \u00e0 la d\u00e9tresse pour soulager les autres, mais de suivre une r\u00e8gle d\u2019\u00e9galit\u00e9: dans la circonstance pr\u00e9sente votre superflu pourvoira \u00e0 leurs besoins,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.14","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.12","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.14","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:14","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>afin que leur superflu pourvoie pareillement aux v\u00f4tres, en sorte qu\u2019il y ait \u00e9galit\u00e9,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.15","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.13","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.15","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:15","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>selon qu\u2019il est \u00e9crit: Celui qui avait ramass\u00e9 beaucoup n\u2019avait rien de trop, et celui qui avait ramass\u00e9 peu n\u2019en manquait pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.16","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.14","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.16","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:16","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.017,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 16-24: cf. 1 Co 16:1-4. 2 Co 9:1-5. 1 Co 14:40.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Gr\u00e2ces soient rendues \u00e0 Dieu de ce qu\u2019il a mis dans le c\u0153ur de Tite le m\u00eame empressement pour vous;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.17","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.15","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.17","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:17","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>car il a accueilli notre demande, et c\u2019est avec un nouveau z\u00e8le et de son plein gr\u00e9 qu\u2019il part pour aller chez vous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.18","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.16","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.18","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:18","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Nous envoyons avec lui le fr\u00e8re dont la louange en ce qui concerne l\u2019\u00c9vangile est r\u00e9pandue dans toutes les \u00c9glises,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.19","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.17","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.19","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:19","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>et qui, de plus, a \u00e9t\u00e9 choisi par les \u00c9glises pour \u00eatre notre compagnon de voyage dans cette \u0153uvre de bienfaisance, que nous accomplissons \u00e0 la gloire du Seigneur m\u00eame et en t\u00e9moignage de notre bonne volont\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.20","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.18","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.20","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:20","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Nous agissons ainsi, afin que personne ne nous bl\u00e2me au sujet de cette abondante collecte, \u00e0 laquelle nous donnons nos soins;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.21","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.19","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.21","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:21","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>car nous recherchons ce qui est bien, non seulement devant le Seigneur, mais aussi devant les hommes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.22","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.20","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.22","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:22","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Nous envoyons avec eux notre fr\u00e8re, dont nous avons souvent \u00e9prouv\u00e9 le z\u00e8le dans beaucoup d\u2019occasions, et qui en montre plus encore cette fois \u00e0 cause de sa grande confiance en vous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.23","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.21","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.23","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:23","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.008.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Ainsi, pour ce qui est de Tite, il est notre associ\u00e9 et notre compagnon d\u2019\u0153uvre aupr\u00e8s de vous; et pour ce qui est de nos fr\u00e8res, ils sont les envoy\u00e9s des \u00c9glises, la gloire de Christ.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.24","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.22","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.24","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 8:24","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.009.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.8.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Donnez-leur donc, \u00e0 la face des \u00c9glises, la preuve de votre charit\u00e9, et montrez-leur que nous avons sujet de nous glorifier de vous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.1","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.23","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocumen